      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMAZING BUNDY (1) bolted in last time, scoring by 4 lengths in slick time (17.45) to take a Grade 5 in a new PB this course and distance. Has the ability and expected to go close again. DOUGLAS (2) led all the way last time out to score by 5 lengths (17.59) at Richmond Straight in a Grade 5 over 324m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. GUNNELL GIRL (8) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (17.70) at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to her name from eight starts. Leading chance. WONDER KID (4) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
